# Environment Variables Template - SECURE VERSION
# ⚠️  SECURITY WARNING: Never put actual secrets in this file!
# Use secret references instead (1Password, Infisical, etc.)

# ==============================================================================
# SECURITY BEST PRACTICES FOR .env FILES
# ==============================================================================
# 1. Use secret manager references instead of plaintext values
# 2. Run your app with: op run -- npm start (for 1Password)
# 3. Or use: infisical run -- npm start (for Infisical)
# 4. Never commit actual .env files with secrets
# ==============================================================================

# API Configuration
# Override the default API base URL if needed
# Development default: /api (uses proxy)
# Production default: https://happyrow-core.onrender.com
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://happyrow-core.onrender.com

# Development Settings
NODE_ENV=development

# GitHub Pages Deployment (automatically set by GitHub Actions)
# VITE_BASE_URL=/happyrow-front/

# Optional: Analytics or monitoring
# VITE_ANALYTICS_ID=your-analytics-id

# Optional: Feature flags
# VITE_ENABLE_DEBUG=true

